            "id": 6383124,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 汎銓(6830)股價殺至跌停，跌停價349.5元，成交1,039張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>汎銓(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6830:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6830\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6830-TW</a>)13日13:20下跌38.5元，股價跌停報349.5元，委賣102張，成交1,039張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為技術分析服務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>汎銓(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6830:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6830\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6830-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲7.33%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.27%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-360 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-252 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-64 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-44 張</li> <li>融資增減：-206 張</li> <li>融券增減：-505 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
